The paper deals with face recognition and presentation attack detection, which are topics related to computer vision (cs.CV) and cybersecurity (cs.CR). The proposed approach involves the use of deep neural networks (cs.LG) and meta learning classifiers (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper uses datasets for evaluation (cs.MM). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CV, followed by cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.MM, and cs.AI.
